\cf9 \cb10 \strokec9 Unfortunately, in computer technology, for interacting with software, these two activities\'a0\cf9 \cb1 \strokec9 \
\cf9 \cb10 \strokec9 have been merged into a single location, most obviously on the mouse but also on\
